      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "今はちゃんと装着しています。ですからさっき\n{user}さんと呼んだじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 32.0358953953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　……あ、確かに\nいやぁ、mihoさんがまたぶつかってるからてっきり",
      "startTime": 37.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
